Package: linux-image-5.10.234-melt
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux kernel for Android Generic Kernel Image (5.10.234-melt)
 This package contains the Linux kernel for the Android Generic Kernel Image (5.10.234-melt) device.
 .
 Note: This package only ships the kernel image and modules, you should probably
 look at the linux-bootimage-5.10.234-melt package for a bootimage suitable
 for Android boot loaders.

Package: linux-bootimage-5.10.234-melt
